title: [Catacombs, Sewers]
description: Heaps of warped and withered wood litter the ground.

Heaps of warped and withered wood litter the ground.  Sections of the old tracks used to carry rocks and other minerals to the outside are visible from underneath the rubbish.  A twisted, slender pipe runs the length of the western wall.  Drops of water seep from a small hole in the pipe, which is creating a small pool of mud.
